{
  "texts": [
    "Co-evolution provides information about the interactions between amino acids in the new protein.",
    "Geometric constraints provide information about the spatial arrangement of amino acids in the new protein.",
    "The development of this AI tool is substantial in drug discovery as it helped solve the structure of nearly 200 million proteins, that is ~ 98.5% of the proteins in the human body (Tunyasuvunakool et al. 2021).",
    "Together with the European Bioinformatics Institute (EMBL-EBI), a database called AlphaFold DB (https:// alpha fold. ebi.",
    "uk/) is created to store all the structures solved so far with AlphaFold."
  ]
}